Once all the login and creating the user is successfully done then we move to the role configuration thing

Roles are defined according to the various users like admin, sales manager, distributor, slaes master and so on

new role can be configured using the edit button available in the portal an dwe can view the things using the view eye button

some roles and there features what they can access and what they can't access are

---------> Finance admin access -> have the main power which is the admin access of the whole system

---------> similarly the roles are assigned according to the varios role and responsibilities with the limited permissions
